  "name": "RPlog_Corellia_Prison_Break",
  "title": "Corellia Prison Break",
  "summary": "At the Coronet City spaceport, a routine day of visiting dignitaries erupts into chaos when a prison transport shuttle crash-lands and thirteen armed prisoners break loose, with the pilot Booster Dustrunner gunned down after sabotaging the controls. Caught in the crossfire are the down-on-her-luck technician Selko and the Quarren mechanic Druze, both terrible shots, alongside Corellian Prime Minister Dash Blazer's CorSec detail. Imperium Moff Liza Molokai and Caspian Presav Crestian Tarasar, joined by the Horansi warrior Kasha and the droid Colonel V1C3, wade into the fight, while the Imperator Tyler Damion (Darth Malign) and the aged Grand Admiral Drayson Honos set up a field medical station and Malign casually Force-chokes and lightsabers attackers. Through a mix of luck, blasters, and blades, the defenders steadily subdue the prisoners, Blazer himself is shot but survives, and the escape collapses. Crestian quietly orders Caspian Intelligence to investigate, suspecting the whole break and the convenient shooting of Blazer were part of a coordinated plot.",
